      "label": "Your Answer",
      "height": "100pt"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading4",
      "text": "What's harsh or uncomfortable about this place?"
    },
    {
      "type": "hint",
      "text": "What do people endure or complain about? What takes getting used to?"
