    {
      "type": "heading2",
      "text": "Climate, Weather & Seasons"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading4",
      "text": "What's the overall climate?"
    },
    {
      "type": "hint",
      "text": "Tropical, temperate, arid, polar? How does it shape what people wear, build, and grow?"
    },
    {
      "type": "writing_box",
      "label": "Your Answer",
      "height": "100pt"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading4",
      "text": "What seasons exist and how distinct are they?"
    },
    {
      "type": "hint",
      "text": "Traditional four seasons? A long winter and brief summer? Magical seasons tied to something other than the sun?"
    },
    {
      "type": "writing_box",
      "label": "Your Answer",
      "height": "100pt"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading4",
      "text": "What season is your story set in?"
    },
    {
      "type": "hint",
      "text": "Seasons create mood and constraint. What does this season make possible for your romance? What does it prevent?"
